          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1690801943694-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1690801943694-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1690801943694-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>haddock filling </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (use individual ones for fancy presentation!) and top with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the dish[es] in the oven and cook for 12-15 min or until bubbling and golden and the fish is cooked through – this is your<strong> haddock smokie</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1690801948347-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1690801948347-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1690801948347-x700.jpg",
