          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1690801948347-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the haddock smokie is nearly ready, slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Once the haddock smokie is ready, remove the dish[es] from the oven and top with your <strong>smoked sea salt flakes</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
